reviewText: As described. So far so good. Many reviews were not as good on this. I have had no problem. I am on the first disc.
I was a young teen when this show came out and it is a delight to revisit that era.  Well packaged, too.
Nice metal collector case. Promptly delivered.
Route 66 is one of the best tv shows ever made!
This is in a beautiful tin. I falsely assumed that the technical quality would have been enhanced and such enhancement is really needed.  The series is great though, just as I remembered it being.
The person I bought this for Loved, Loved, Loved it. Good price, fast shipping, packed well and exactly as described. Thank you!!! 5* seller'
delivered in time alloted and great quality.
